attributeValues.value: Crafted from smooth matte jersey, this sophisticated dress from American Living features luxe satin trim and a dramatic cascading ruffle.
Shaping darts at bust; satin trim detail at the waist gathers into a cascading ruffle at the left side
Lined at the bodice and back of skirt
